Hey! I’m the creator of houndutil. If you are checking out the RustHOUNDS code for this year, run:

git submodule init --update

This will also pull down the submodule that we use to expedite our programming process!

To fix the IntelliSense errors, run the “Clean Java Language Server Workspace” command after pulling down the submodule.

If you need additional help, feel free to message me!
